---
name: Update OCSF OSINT Context
description: |
  Periodically fetches alphaMountain threats and updates the shared
  `ocsf-osint` lookup table from the Tenzir utilities package.
---

every 1h {
  alphamountain::threat::feed license="ALPHAMOUNTAIN_LICENSE"
  alphamountain::ocsf::map
  tenzir::osint::update_context max_age=30d
}
